            <title>[CASSANDRA-7319] Fix availability validation for LOCAL_ONE CL</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-7319</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;ConsistencyLevel#assureSufficientLiveNodes() is currently broken wrt LOCAL_ONE (unlike ConsistencyLevel#isSufficientLiveNodes()). Because of this it&apos;s possible for a read request to go to a node in a non-local DC if there are no live replicas in the local DC (writes are also affected).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
